{"tid":1018200,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有應徵者竟然將一年工作經驗寫上CV","createTime":"2019-02-12T05:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T06:04:25.000Z","uid":196627,"like":34,"dislike":1821,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"cee8709d4efc1eccd23158a127504c0a74ec9359","tid":1018200,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"最近我公司想請個新會計文員<br />\n而小妹係做HR主任既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁係希望幫老細搵到正正常常既人啦<br />\n點知我前兩日收到份CV<br />\n我一睇...<br />\n犀利喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢起一間叫畢馬威既大型會計師行<br />\n做auditor喎<br />\n點知我再睇落去...<br />\n佢2015年入職<br />\n只係得一年工作經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難得入到畢馬威呢D大公司<br />\n竟然做左一年就辭職<br />\n呢D後生仔個腦究竟諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是我咪約左佢今日黎面試啦<br />\n<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢:<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我﹕點解你做左一年就辭職呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢﹕我間公司最近生意唔好，所以我老細咪暗示想我主動走囉。<br />\n(咁離譜既excuse都比佢講得出，條友係咪未食藥呀)<br />\n<br />\n我﹕畢馬威大公司黎架喎，咁都會生意唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢﹕我間公司之前無左幾個大客，所以我老細咪想cut人囉<br />\n<br />\n我﹕咁你表現好咪唔會比人cut囉，你老細咁講好明顯係你自己能力有問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢﹕咁我間公司好睇員工既資歷。咁我資歷淺既，梗係cut我先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我﹕咁你成間公司既Junior係唔係全部比人勸退晒呀?明明係你自己表現差，仲要起度死撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢﹕......(比我串到啞左)<br />\n<br />\n我﹕我地只係會請D有責任心，肯學肯做既人囉。你資質差都算啦。但係你依家又 Jumpy、又鐘意搵藉口......你問下你自己適唔適合起我地公司做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我見佢頭dupdup<br />\n眼濕濕咁樣<br />\n然後垂頭喪氣咁樣走左啦"},{"pid":"95b3be3c10b61984c68e1507e087e8b0e1789ce9","tid":1018200,"uid":162866,"like":458,"dislike":17,"score":441,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFbFrKb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFbFrKb.jpg&h=7e4b1ede&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e24085b11241af363a970cff409772a84efee266","tid":1018200,"uid":8439,"like":202,"dislike":5,"score":197,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"樓豬真係好人 仲肯教精佢"},{"pid":"a189a5cb5a4d9f308579ac85d050360cb0c689ac","tid":1018200,"uid":196627,"like":15,"dislike":615,"score":-600,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:24:58.000Z","msg":"我個post完全唔係for笑<br />\n公司目的係利潤最大化<br />\n目的係警惕所有應徵者<br />\n幫大部分幼稚連登仔建立正確工作價值觀<br />\n要笑既可以正評後出翻去"},{"pid":"a2475d58d8061f463dfd3c6a84bf5752e82bda5a","tid":1018200,"uid":106426,"like":706,"dislike":4,"score":702,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1ad49c93259e0af627bdc311e7c636d73f4621e","tid":1018200,"uid":10287,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:27:23.000Z","msg":"未轉ac呀"},{"pid":"6706424edc1b4ce190e5bf628967bc3759a01509","tid":1018200,"uid":171594,"like":109,"dislike":1,"score":108,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"個個post結尾都一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8feab27bdd07f23205f3f2310ef3c1affda92db","tid":1018200,"uid":228143,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:27:59.000Z","msg":"仲未入正題<br />\nｇａｙ故？"},{"pid":"f61bb7fffccbd9c152feb209011f0c1330f6865f","tid":1018200,"uid":26711,"like":328,"dislike":3,"score":325,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"Mary, 你陣間入一入我房<br />\n同你講過幾多次大行黎既人要比我親自in?"},{"pid":"290461523010961f71621b7ad31742a0944bee4b","tid":1018200,"uid":69976,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:29:05.000Z","msg":"0/99999999999999"},{"pid":"1e6cf8940664e3c65f219d5d58d0253f5f39c444","tid":10182