br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBetween 屌爆你老母呀成日開膠post 祝你過唔到十五呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c21458238827cad7ccca5b865c40792b7f60a03","tid":1018200,"uid":18417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"HR 根本就係一個笑話, 我覺得如果要炒, 第一個部門就應該先炒哂班HR"},{"pid":"a665bd21f4dea6510fab28539f196a62bcde0838","tid":1018200,"uid":740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:33:10.000Z","msg":"jumpy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc32d1394f1dc9f0bd5db6d1696fd620c9846d1","tid":1018200,"uid":164501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a665bd21f4dea6510fab28539f196a62bcde0838","tid":1018200,"uid":740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:33:10.000Z","msg":"jumpy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:37:36.000Z","msg":"有套戲叫JUMPER <br />\n樓豬岩睇 廧徵者咁勁 咁JUMPY 應該唔岩做佢呢D 垃圾工"},{"pid":"d4b2d52a11652413ed94f7793c85829594caf970","tid":1018200,"uid":196964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"Jumpy？查下字典先啦"},{"pid":"ded9bc9a119c7aca9b994924267b7269f0213227","tid":1018200,"uid":170886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee8709d4efc1eccd23158a127504c0a74ec9359","tid":1018200,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"最近我公司想請個新會計文員<br />\n而小妹係做HR主任既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁係希望幫老細搵到正正常常既人啦<br />\n點知我前兩日收到份CV<br />\n我一睇...<br />\n犀利喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢起一間叫畢馬威既大型會計師行<br />\n做auditor喎<br />\n點知我再睇落去...<br />\n佢2015年入職<br />\n只係得一年工作經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難得入到畢馬威呢D大公司<br />\n竟然做左一年就辭職<br />\n呢D後生仔個腦究竟諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是我咪約左佢今日黎面試啦<br />\n<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢:<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我﹕點解你做左一年就辭職呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢﹕我間公司最近生意唔好，所以我老細咪暗示想我主動走囉。<br />\n(咁離譜既excuse都比佢講得出，條友係咪未食藥呀)<br />\n<br />\n我﹕畢馬威大公司黎架喎，咁都會生意唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢﹕我間公司之前無左幾個大客，所以我老細咪想cut人囉<br />\n<br />\n我﹕咁你表現好咪唔會比人cut囉，你老細咁講好明顯係你自己能力有問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢﹕咁我間公司好睇員工既資歷。咁我資歷淺既，梗係cut我先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我﹕咁你成間公司既Junior係唔係全部比人勸退晒呀?明明係你自己表現差，仲要起度死撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢﹕......(比我串到啞左)<br />\n<br />\n我﹕我地只係會請D有責任心，肯學肯做既人囉。你資質差都算啦。但係你依家又 Jumpy、又鐘意搵藉口......你問下你自己適唔適合起我地公司做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我見佢頭dupdup<br />\n眼濕濕咁樣<br />\n然後垂頭喪氣咁樣走左啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:56:15.000Z","msg":"0/10 咁既垃圾故<br />\n除左呃下負評上熱門,有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c2785f063e483548be1230c988fc61c80e426b","tid":1018200,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:00:00.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"d681fd92e1c26fd6bada2afe447f4ff0578afe5f","tid":1018200,"uid":23058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:03:18.000Z","msg":"行內人點會用中文名 KPMG 就KPMG 你講畢馬威一時三刻都唔知你噏乜柒"},{"pid":"ce728b6cd00551e4fe0111e2f53fcbb34dba327f","tid":1018200,"uid":201552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"做hr做到成日出post喺度笑啲應徵者，你都幾得閒，最應該解僱嘅，應該係樓主同成個hr<img 